175
00:15:36,230 --> 00:15:38,650
Čo s mojou sukňou?

176
00:15:40,060 --> 00:15:42,930
Nemáš zazipsovaný zips.

177
00:15:52,580 --> 00:15:54,540
Otoč sa.

178
00:15:54,540 --> 00:15:57,200
To je v poriadku. Zvládnem to sama.

179
00:15:58,360 --> 00:16:00,130
Nepochybne.

180
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:26,520
Statická elektrina. Fyzika základnej školy.

181
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:30,570
