857
01:10:32,510 --> 01:10:34,380
Li Jin Qin?

858
01:10:36,180 --> 01:10:38,380
Ty si Li Jin Qin?

859
01:10:40,060 --> 01:10:42,490
Ja som ten Li Jin Qin.

